reviewText: If you are a fan of ET, I heartily recommend this DVD. The quality was good, considering the age of the original. A little pricey, but, worth it if you are a fan of Ernest Tubb.
Can't beat Ernest Tubb. He's a great singer and knows how to entertain.
I purchased this for my father who is a big fan of Ernest Tubb, I was so disappointed when the DVD was so snowy it was barely viewable.
